title: Aloha 'Oe
lyrics:
[intro] (F) (C) (G7) (C-G7)

Ha 'a(C)heo ka(F)ua ina (C)pali 
Ke (G7)nihi a'ela i ka nahele
E a(C)hai ana (F)paha i ka (C)liko 
Pua (F)a'hihi (G7)lehua o (C)uka (C7)

A(F)loha 'oe, a(C)loha 'oe 
E ke (G7)onaona noho i ka (C)li(C7)po 
One (F)fond embrace, a (C)ho 'i a 'e au 
Un(G7)til we meet a(C)gain
